headline: Is EQT Still Attractive After Strong Multi Year Gains And Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: Wondering if EQT is still a smart way to play natural gas, or if the easy money has already been made? This breakdown will help you decide whether the current price matches the underlying value. Even after a recent pullback of 6.7% over the last week and 7.6% over the last month, EQT is still up 18.4% year to date, 23.7% over the last year, and a huge 341.8% over five years, which says a lot about how the market’s view of the company has evolved. Those swings are happening against a backdrop...
